songs.title: Demon Stuck in Your Eye
songs.lyrics:
You've got the water stuck in your mouth
You want to take it up but you just don't know how
You've got the demon stuck in your eye
You want to get him out but you just don't know why

You've got the demon stuck in your eye
You want to get him out but you just don't know why
You've got the water stuck in your mouth
You want to head, head, head south

When in mind you can't believe this maze you're in
Need a hand or two to breathe through this man
Understand this love I have for you man
Need a hand or two to see it's you
Can't you see it's you
